# Arvasit Auth SDK

[![npm version](https://badge.fury.io/js/@pratik_25%2Fauth-sdk.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/js/@pratik_25%2Fauth-sdk)
[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/arvasit-auth-sdk.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/arvasit-auth-sdk)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

This repository contains the official Arvasit Authentication SDK for Node.js and Python, providing comprehensive authentication services including user management, two-factor authentication, password management, and login activity monitoring.

## üöÄ Features

- **User Authentication**: Signup, login with password/OTP, and logout
- **Two-Factor Authentication**: Complete 2FA setup, verification, and management
- **Password Management**: Forgot password, password reset, and password updates
- **Recovery Codes**: Generate and manage recovery codes for account access
- **Login Activity**: Track and monitor user login activities
- **Type Safety**: Full type definitions for both TypeScript and Python
- **Schema-Driven**: Single JSON schema generates both SDKs automatically
- **Magic Link Authentication**: Passwordless login via email links

## üìÅ Project Structure

```
arva-auth-sdk/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ schemas/                    # Single source of truth
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ auth-types.json        # JSON schema definitions
